you have to get a fresh turtle (1-2kg)
boil a whole pot of water with 5L, add a pinch of salt and olive oil
when boiling, add the turtle
heat the ove to 225C
get flour, eggs and sugar and do the dough
after 45 min tkae the turtle out, and get the breast and legs, peel them get all the meat
mince the meat and mix with brown sugar - let it rest for 15min
put the meat in the dough and put it in the oven for 45min
take it out, let it join 10min and ENJOY
